            <description><![CDATA[【转给更多人！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E6%97%B6%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%87%AA%E6%95%91%E9%80%83%E7%94%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E6%97%B6%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%87%AA%E6%95%91%E9%80%83%E7%94%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#地震发生时如何自救逃生#</span></a>】北京时间8月6日2时33分山东德州市平原县发生5.5级地震。截至6日7时，地震已致至少20人轻微伤。在室内或室外避震怎么做？哪种求生姿势最有效？戳图<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E8%AF%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E8%87%AA%E6%95%91%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E8%AF%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E8%87%AA%E6%95%91%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#每个人都该掌握的地震自救知识#</span></a>👇🏻（人民日报） <img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgmvx93xstj20j60kz0y3.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgmvx9lcnvj20j60srn41.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgmvx8c1h4j20j60jytdd.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgmvxabr2vj20j10j1jw1.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgn0421r7pj20fq0fqtb9.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgn042b7dqj20j60l0jwd.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgn042mxnij20j60kxwjd.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgn04402dij20j60jr797.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgn044vmmrj20j60o8tej.jpg" re