            <description><![CDATA[【学起！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%232%E4%B8%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E5%B8%AE%E5%8A%A9%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E9%A9%BC%E8%83%8C%23&amp;extparam=%232%E4%B8%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E5%B8%AE%E5%8A%A9%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E9%A9%BC%E8%83%8C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#2个动作帮助改善驼背#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[全力以赴]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/d9/2023_fighting_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[全力以赴]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/d9/2023_fighting_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】第一个动作：用力用手夹紧身体，然后背部发力，向外转动手臂，每天大概30下；第二个动作：双手抱住后脑勺，然后靠近墙壁，用手肘支撑墙壁向上拉伸维持5秒，每天大概20下👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> （浙大邵逸夫医院骨科徐文斌） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4930984454324235" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">人民日报的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/0033ImPzly1hgkkv2gc0pj60u01hcq6602.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/6KIfqPEwlx087xpsOOgM01041200gEqA0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691396886&amp;ssig=Ob1d1I2HaQ&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/8Ywk6VFLlx087xpucOcw01041200agey0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=16913968