            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>周知！暴雨洪水过后，这些事千万不能大意！】暴雨洪水除了带来泥石流、滑坡等灾害，还会污染水源和引发传染病疫情，即使暴雨和洪水退去也不可掉以轻心。不要喝生水及地下水、不吃被洪水浸泡过的食物，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%B4%E8%BF%87%E5%90%8E%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E8%A6%81%E5%BD%BB%E5%BA%95%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%81%E5%92%8C%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%B4%E8%BF%87%E5%90%8E%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E8%A6%81%E5%BD%BB%E5%BA%95%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%81%E5%92%8C%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#洪水过后房屋要彻底清洁和消毒#</span></a>，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%A8%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%B4%E8%BF%87%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%8F%8A%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%A8%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%B4%E8%BF%87%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%8F%8A%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#暴雨洪水过后的安全及防疫提醒#</span></a>👇🏻（人民日报） <img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hglnw18bdgj20rs102jwk.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hglnw2ohmuj20rs102q7s.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hglnw40dfpj20rs0xmjvi.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hglnw5iq6aj20rs0xm0x4.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hglnw7eoipj20rs14odls.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hglr39y06ej20rs0xmn1v.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hglr38otvqj20rs0xmtdc.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hglnvzq8vvj20rs102af0.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hglr3aaiufj20rs11z43l.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
